. 
<emphasis box="[746,832,835,859]" italics="true" pageId="112" pageNumber="111">daviesi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
but distinguished from that species by yellowish brown legs, male genitalia with sides rounded throughout, female spermathecal capsule abruptly bent in basal 1/3; and Brazilian 
<typeStatus box="[519,572,900,924]" pageId="112" pageNumber="111">type</typeStatus>
locality.
</paragraph>
